									<div class="description author withsidebar">
										<h6><a href="https://lithub.com/author/lisakaltenegger/">Lisa Kaltenegger</a></h6>
										Dr. Lisa Kaltenegger is the Director of the Carl Sagan Institute to search for life in the cosmos at Cornell and Associate Professor in Astronomy. Her book <em>Alien Earths: The New Science of Planet Hunting in the Cosmos</em> is out now from St. Martin’s Press.																			</div>
								</div><br class="clear"/><br/>
							</div>
							<br class="clear"/>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div>
